"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector=self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector||[]).push([[475],{5232(e,a,t){t.r(a),t.d(a,{comp:()=>r,data:()=>h});var i=t(641);const l=t.p+"assets/img/installation-add-new-e1594061377561.fcbf7267.webp",n=t.p+"assets/img/installation-upload-plugin-e1594057787105.383818ff.webp",o=t.p+"assets/img/install.372d397e.webp",s={},r=(0,t(6262).A)(s,[["render",function(e,a){return(0,i.uX)(),(0,i.CE)("div",null,[...a[0]||(a[0]=[(0,i.Fv)('<h1 id="installation-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#installation-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector"><span>Installation – WooCommerce eBay Connector</span></a></h1><p>This section allows the admin to install and activate the <strong>WooCommerce eBay Connector</strong> plugin on their WordPress store to begin the synchronization process.</p><hr><h2 id="downloading-the-plugin-zip" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#downloading-the-plugin-zip"><span>Downloading the Plugin ZIP</span></a></h2><p>After purchasing the module, the admin will receive a <strong>ZIP file</strong> containing the plugin data.</p><ul><li>Download the file to your local system.</li><li><strong>Important:</strong> Do <strong>NOT</strong> unzip the file before uploading it to WordPress.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="uploading-the-plugin-to-wordpress" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#uploading-the-plugin-to-wordpress"><span>Uploading the Plugin to WordPress</span></a></h2><p>The admin can upload the plugin through the WordPress dashboard:</p><ul><li>Login to your <strong>WordPress Admin Panel</strong>.</li><li>Navigate to <strong>Plugins → Add New Plugin</strong> in the left sidebar menu.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/installation-add-new-e1594061377561.webp"><img src="'+l+'" alt="Add New Plugin"></a></p><ul><li>Click the <strong>Upload Plugin</strong> button located at the top of the page.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/installation-upload-plugin-e1594057787105.webp"><img src="'+n+'" alt="Upload Plugin"></a></p><ul><li>Click <strong>Choose File</strong> and select the downloaded ZIP file from your system.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/installation-choose-file-e1594057730398.webp"><img src="data:image/webp;base64," alt="Choose File"></a></p><hr><h2 id="installing-the-connector-module" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#installing-the-connector-module"><span>Installing the Connector Module</span></a></h2><ul><li>Once the file is selected, click the <strong>Install Now</strong> button.</li><li>WordPress will automatically upload and extract the plugin files.</li><li>Wait for the installation process to complete.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/install.webp"><img src="'+o+'" alt="Install Now"></a></p><hr><h2 id="activating-the-plugin" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#activating-the-plugin"><span>Activating the Plugin</span></a></h2><ul><li>After a successful installation, click on the <strong>Activate Plugin</strong> button.</li><li>This will enable the eBay Connector features within your WordPress dashboard.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/installation-activate-plugin-e1594057972984.webp"><img src="data:image/webp;base64," alt="Activate Plugin"></a></p><hr><h2 id="license-activation" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#license-activation"><span>License Activation</span></a></h2><p>The admin must validate the module license to receive future updates and support.</p><ul><li>Learn how to activate your license and complete the setup by <a href="https://wpdoc.webkul.com/license-validator/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">clicking here</a>.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="module-translation" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#module-translation"><span>Module Translation</span></a></h2><p>The WooCommerce eBay Connector supports multi-language translation to cater to global regions:</p><ul><li>To translate the module into your preferred language, refer to the <a href="https://webkul.com/blog/how-to-translate-the-woocommerce-plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Webkul Translation Guide</a>.</li><li>This allows the admin to customize labels and text according to local requirements.</li></ul>',31)])])}]]),h=JSON.parse('{"path":"/documentation/installation.html","title":"Installation – WooCommerce eBay Connector","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{"prev":"/documentation/features.html","next":"/documentation/ebay-account-setup.html"},"git":{"contributors":[{"name":"shakir.hussain","username":"","email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","commits":2},{"name":"aadesh","username":"","email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","commits":2}],"changelog":[{"hash":"86ec3d42e91345957915d7d678cf29733245262d","time":1774624521000,"email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","author":"shakir.hussain","message":"updated blog contant"},{"hash":"2d5c39163a248635a79c60d8508c0716b0a11c03","time":1772114569000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"add export product"},{"hash":"a3379ad1acde7722f52940c853addb733657393e","time":1771942912000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"update images"},{"hash":"277c5a1bdc13e06551e102ee26c728b6b048e50b","time":1771481506000,"email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","author":"shakir.hussain","message":"updated ebay blog and move to dev"}]},"filePathRelative":"documentation/installation.md"}')}}]);